content:
To route messaging sessions in a messaging channel, edit the channel, and then specify the routing method and queue for the channel.

Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Professional, Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer Editions with the Service Cloud

From Setup in the Quick Find box, enter Messaging, and then select Messaging Settings.
Under Channels, open and edit the existing messaging channel.
Under Routing, enter the routing properties.
PROPERTY	DESCRIPTION
Enable Advanced Routing	If you want to use Omni-Channel flows, check this checkbox.
Routing Type	Select Omni-Channel.
Queue	Specify the queue to which you want to route messaging sessions in this channel.
Under Automated Responses, enter the consent settings, conversation responses, and help.
Click Save.
title: Service Cloud Routing Guide
